    Abstract class which defines a cell.

    main.CellManager contains redValues,whiteValues, and sickValues.

    A List of main.Constants used thought the classes
    main.GameOverScreen
    Displays to the user a you win or you loose Gif and then displays stats and try again on blue buttons.
    main.HealthBar
    This is a health bar used by all cells to show the health of the cell.
    main.InputHandler
    Handles all the inputs, key inputs, mouse inputs, and mouse movement when shifting the screen.
    test.JUnit
    This class tests all the classes of the project.

    An implementation of the abstract cell.
    main.ScoreBoard
    Keeps track of the seconds elapsed, and the scores: totalScore,whiteCellsKilled,and redCellsConquered.

    main.SickCell is child class (extends) main.Cell abstract class.
    main.Virus
    The main.Virus Class is the main unit that the player controls and uses it to conquer the enemy cells and anti viruses

    main.WelcomeScreen
